# prose_translation = Epic poetry and Tragedy, as well as Comedy, Dithyrambic poetry, and most music for the flute and lyre, are all, viewed as a whole, modes of imitation.
# literal_translation = Epic poetry indeed and the of the tragedy poetry, and further comedy and the dithyramb-making [art] and of the flute-playing the most and of lyre-playing, all happen being imitations as a whole.
